### 6.11 Collapsible Modes

| `collapsible` | Expanded | Collapsed |
|---------------|----------|-----------|
| `"icon"` | Full width (12rem) | Icon-only (3rem) |
| `"offcanvas"` | Full width | Hidden (slides off, gap = 0) |
| `"none"` | Always full width | N/A |

